      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road as soon as you are. Come take it for a spin, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
