      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, a high-revving powerhouse featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and driver engagement. The chassis maintains its precision through Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a weight-optimized aluminum multi-link rear suspension. Preventative maintenance is up to date, with rod bearings and throttle actuators recently addressed to ensure the integrity of the high-tension internals. This example represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with a focus on visceral performance and longitudinal dynamics.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Engine runs well. Interior is clean. Minor exterior wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has enjoyed the open road. It sits on factory alloy wheels with approximately 70% tread remaining on the Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather seats are supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. I have stayed ahead of the service schedule, recently completing a full synthetic oil change, brake fluid flush, and cabin filter replacement within the last 1,500 miles. The engine pulls smoothly through the gears without hesitation, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering a premium driving experience without the 'new car' depreciation. Complete service records and two sets of keys are included.",
      "price": 32500.0,
